# pmi-web configuration moved to the platform-root single source of truth:
#   /Users/reid/micah/pmi_data_platform/.env
#
# This file is kept only as a pointer; Next.js loads env vars from process.env
# inside the running container. docker-compose injects via env_file (the
# consolidated platform-root .env).
#
# pmi-web specifically reads:
#   - NEXT_PUBLIC_PMI_API_URL  (browser-facing, must be reachable from host)
#   - PMI_API_URL              (SSR, uses compose hostname inside containers)
#
# Bootstrap a fresh checkout:
#   cp pmi_data_platform/.env.example pmi_data_platform/.env
